
   Karlos Quake 1.8 release 3

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

   server options data structure, stored in "registered"

   Bit(s)   Name                    Remarks

   0        GAME_REGISTERED         Must be set to 1
   1        GAME_SHRAPNEL
   2        GAME_MIKERULES
   3        GAME_RANDOM             Not yet implemented

   4-7      FUTURE                  Game option expansion

   8-11     FX_LIGHTS               Dynamic light switches
               FX_BRIGHTFIELD          (unused ?)
               FX_FLASH                Flash effects
               FX_BRIGHTLIGHT          (unused ?)
               FX_GLOW                 Glow effects

   12       FX_WORLDSTATIC          Ambient light effects switch

   13       FX_CON_GAMMA            New for 1.8r3 Gamma effects switch
   14       FX_CON_FLASH            Not implemented yet
   15       FX_CON_FOV              New for 1.8r3 Field of View effects switch

   16       FX_FAST_EXP             Fast explosion switch
   17       FX_MULTI_EXP            Multiframe explosion switch
   18       FX_SMART_EXP            Smart explosion switch

   19       FX_SOUND_LIMIT          New for 1.8r3 Sound limiting switch
   20       FX_SOUND_PLUS           Not implemented yet

   21       FX_GORE_BLOOD           New for 1.8r3 Blood effects switch
   22       FX_GORE_GIBS            New for 1.8r3 Giblets effects switch
   23       FX_GORE_CORPSE          New for 1.8r3 Solid corpse effects switch

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

   client options data structure, stored in "temp1"

   Bit(s)   Name                    Remarks

   0-4      <SKIN NUMBER>
   5        CL_GENDERBIT
   6        CL_MESSAGEBIT
   7        CL_INVENTORYBIT
   8        CL_SHOW_TARGETS         New for 1.8r3 Names player/monster under target
   9-11     <ION COLOUR>            New for 1.8r3 Personalised Ion Cannon trail colour
                                    Blue, Red, Magenta, Green, Cyan, Yellow or White ;)

   14       FL_USING_CAMERA
   15       FL_USING_TARGET
   16       FL_USING_TORCH
   17       FL_USING_GUIDE
   18       FL_USING_GRAPPLE        New for 1.8r3 Use Rocket as grapple by default
   19       FL_USING_ION            New for 1.8r3 Use thunderbolt as Ion Cannon by default

